          "brief_html": "<blockquote>\n<p><strong>LEARNING OBJECTIVES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compute $\\phi(n) = (p-1)(q-1)$ for RSA.</li>\n<li>Choose public exponent $e$ coprime to $\\phi(n)$.</li>\n<li>Derive private exponent $d \\equiv e^{-1} \\pmod{\\phi(n)}$.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n"
